Package: mixstream
Type: Package
Title: Mixture Modelling in Data Streams
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2015-05-31
Authors@R: person("Jordan", "Noble", email="jn610@imperial.ac.uk",
                  role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: MixStream implements online algorithms for parameter estimation of
  finite mixture models. The online EM algorithm is used to estimate the
  parameters of mixtures of exponential families and SGD (stochastic gradient
  descent) is used to estimate the regression coefficients for finite mixtures
  of generalised linear models. Moreover, MixStream provides a general framework
  that allows users to specify their own mixture models.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
  stream,
  mvtnorm
ByteCompile: TRUE